## How to add a row

1. Run `/hypothesis-register "<your pain point>"`.
2. The skill walks you through 8 steps including required kill-criteria.
3. Approve to write — never hand-edit. Skill writes BOTH the summary row + the detail block.

## Why this artifact exists

Without explicit kill-criteria, agentic experiments drag past viability. ADLC's signature discipline: hypothesis → PoV → hard go/no-go. See `docs/research/ADLC-source.md` (vendored EPAM extract) for source rationale.
